  <title>Globals Window</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Globals Window</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">On the Globals window you can see a global variables in your app and the referenced class libraries that are loaded from your app.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="debugger-Globals.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">When your app does not include the X# runtime then a message will be shown that the runtime has not been loaded:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="debugger-Globals-NoRuntime.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
  </body>
